text: Phymorhynchus n. sp. “SWIR” is a species of yet udescibed (as of 2016) sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Raphitomidae. ==Distribution== This species is known only from Longqi vent field in Southwest Indian Ridge. ==Description== ==References== ==External links== Category:Phymorhynchus Category:Undescribed gastropod species
title: Phymorhynchus n. sp. “SWIR”
